{"tid":682262,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Star Lord來華po與吳京合照：等不及看《戰狼3》了","createTime":"2018-05-28T17:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T16:48:54.000Z","uid":66943,"like":4,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"979ae2a85c5120d7cd6391dd82dbeeb75f03f305","tid":682262,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T17:15:37.000Z","msg":"在MCU中飾演&ldquo;Star Lord&rdquo;的Chris Pratt目前正在中國為其新電影《Jurassic World : Fallen Kingdom》做宣傳，今天他也在微博po了一張與吳京的合照，並表示已經等不及要看《戰狼3》了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/upimg/pic/2018/05/28/origin_201805282215226396.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fupimg%2Fpic%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2Forigin_201805282215226396.jpg&h=afd8d4cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nChris Pratt微博原文如下：<br />\n<br />\n　　我非常有幸能和&ldquo;戰狼&rdquo;吳京一起共進晚餐，已經等不及要看續作《戰狼3》了！而說到續作&hellip;&hellip;感謝大家在上海的歡迎，我們在討論的環節體驗到了非常多的樂趣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img1.gamersky.com/upimg/pic/2018/05/28/origin_201805282216047406.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg1.gamersky.com%2Fupimg%2Fpic%2F2018%2F05%2F28%2Forigin_201805282216047406.jpg&h=d329935f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《Jurassic World : Fallen Kingdom》即將在6月15日正式上映，該片由Chris Pratt和Bryce Dallas Howard主演，Steven Allan Spielberg擔任製片。"},{"pid":"90f9b19780068e6b718e7d3e862c689cb36646ef","tid":682262,"uid":29702,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T17:19:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dc96eb6304855ab0d8d6bae50774e320ba67e41c","tid":682262,"uid":106950,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T17:40:29.000Z","msg":"吳京大腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb6580a75a8a81225c9faf33fdbfb029ec3c0837","tid":682262,"uid":66943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T23:42:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a903bd6d8bae0